       # OSU Meet up
       In March we joined the digital Meet up of iGEM OSU. A lot of iGEM teams from all over the world were part of it. 
       We discussed with a lot of teams where to start with their project and how to participate in the competition. 
       In addition to that, we got to know our cooperation partners iGEM Tue, iGEM Düsseldorf, and iGEM Bonn.
       
       # International Survey about GMOs
       In May we met with iGEM Maastricht. They asked if we are interested in creating a survey about GMOs with iGEM IISER Tirupati and iGEM IISER Pune. 
       In a few meetings, we designed a questionnaire with specific questions about the topics the different teams were working on. 
       We were really interested in how the attitude towards GMOs changes depending on age and education.
